xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd" fromDate="{$getProcessList/filter/created/between/fromDate/text()}" optional="true" toDate="{$getProcessList/filter/created/between/toDate/text()}"/> </ns:created> <ns:completed> <ns1:on xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd">{$getProcessList/filter/completed/on/text()}</ns1:on> <ns1:between xmlns:ns1="http://schemas.active-endpoints.com/engineapi/2010/05/EngineAPITypes.xsd" fromDate="{$getProcessList/filter/completed/between/fromDate/text()}" optional="true" toDate="{$getProcessList/filter/completed/between/toDate/text()}"/> </ns:completed> <ns:processGroup>{$getProcessList/filter/processGroup/text()}</ns:processGroup> <ns:hideSystem>{$getProcessList/filter/hideSystem/text()}</ns:hideSystem> <ns:advancedQuery>{$getProcessList/filter/advancedQuery/text()}</ns:advancedQuery> <ns:hidePublicTenant>{$getProcessList/filter/hidePublicTenant/text()}</ns:hidePublicTenant> </ns:filter> else if(boolean($getProcessList/processIdFilter)) then <ns:processIdFilter> { for $processId in $getProcessList/processIdFilter/processId return <ns:processId>{$processId/text()}</ns:processId> } </ns:processIdFilter> else () } </ns:getProcessList> </soap:Body> </soap:Envelope>
